<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>21</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zaangfahnak hri tlai in, Lungthin hmunkhat tein, Jesuh thawngin
 pumkhat kan si, Vancung bantuk a si.

[V2]
 Kan Pa thutnak hmaiah, Lung khat in kan i pum, Kan ruahchannak kha aa
 khat ko, Lunglawmhnak kha a tam.

[V3]
 Ngaihchiatnak kan i hrawm, Thilrit zong kan i hrawm, Khi bantuk Bawipa
 phung kan zulh, Thluachuahnak kan hmuh cio.

[V4]
 Kan i then than tikah, Ngaihchiatnak kha a tam; Siseh kan ruahchannak
 van ah, Ton thannak a um lai.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>ZAANGFAHNAK HRI TLAI IN CH21</title>
</song>